{"type":"message","id":"890978b4","parentId":"fbe87596","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:00:12.862Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.read:10","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nproposal_id: kublai-20260310-015952\nagent: kublai\ndomain: Routing, coordination, cross-agent orchestration\ncreated: 2026-03-10T01:59:52.013919\nstatus: pending\nvoting_deadline: 2026-03-10T02:00:00\nimpact: high\neffort: medium\n---\n\n# Proposal: Implement Proposal-Based Task Routing\n\n## Domain\nRouting, coordination, cross-agent orchestration\n\n## Problem Statement\nTasks are sometimes routed to agents outside their expertise due to keyword overlap.\n\n## Proposed Solution\nAdd a proposal review step where agents can accept or reject tasks before execution.\n\n## Expected Impact\nReduce misroutes by 50%, improve agent autonomy, better task-agent matching.\n\n## Implementation Steps\n1. Add task acceptance workflow\n2. Create rejection reason tracking\n3. Update routing algorithm with feedback\n4. Monitor misroute reduction\n\n## Resource Requirements\n4-6 hours development, ongoing monitoring\n\n## Risk Assessment\nMedium risk - may increase latency, requires agent buy-in\n\n## Success Metrics\n- Misroute rate reduced by 50%\n- Task completion time not increased\n- Agent satisfaction improved\n\n---\n*Generated by kublai at 2026-03-10T01:59:52.013919*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773122412841}}
